trict turnaround times\n\nOther duties as assigned\n\n\nQUALIFICATIONS\n\n\n1-2 year(s) experience with offline captioning in a broadcast setting and editing experience preferred\n\nStrong typing skill with a WPM speed of 70 or greater required\n\nMinimum of a high school diploma required, bachelor\u2019s degree preferred, but not required.\n\nAbility to sit and focus for extended periods of time while captioning & monitoring incoming videos\n\nStrong command of the English language\n\nStrong attention to detail and the ability to manage multiple daily deadlines\n\nAbility to work on-site at our headquarters in State College, Pennsylvania\n\nFlexibility with working varying shifts; First, Second and Third shift coverage for our 24/7 network operations\n\nStrong communication skills\n\n\n\n\nWe are an Equal Opportunity Employer. We provide equal opportunity to all qualified individuals regardless of race, color, religion, age, genetic information, gender, gender expression or identity, sexual orientation, national origin, veteran orientation, or veteran status, pregnancy, disability, marital status or any other legally protected categories under local, state of federal laws.\nWe believe a culture of diversity and inclusion provides unique perspectives that help make the workplace more innovative, engaging and profitable.", "job_location": "State College, PA", "job_title": "Closed Captioning Specialist I", "job_url": "https://boards.greenhouse.io/accuweather/jobs/1945061", "seen_time_epoch": 1577549228, "short_description": null, "tags_string": null}
